author: SitefinityUX Team <SitefinityUX@telerik.com>
name: bootstrap
description: This package is based on the [Bootstrap framework](http://getbootstrap.com/) . In order to use it you need to add the package to the ResourcePackages folder of your project. If the ResourcePackages folder doesn't contain any packages, widget templates will be loaded from Feather or from the MVC folder of SitefinityWebApp (if this folder contains files with names, matching the naming convention). Templates from the source of Feather have lowest loading priority. Templates in the MVC folder of SitefinityWebApp are with higher priority, and templates from a package have highest loading priority.
